-- NYSE Euronext Names Jon Robson as CEO of Technology Division
-- B y   R i t a   N a z a r e t h
-- 2012-09-11T13:14:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-11/nyse-euronext-names-jon-robson-as-ceo-of-technology-division.html
NYSE Euronext (NYX) , the biggest U.S.
exchange operator, named Jon Robson as chief executive officer
of its commercial technology division.  Robson, who will be based in New York, previously held the
position as president of the enterprise division at  Thomson
Reuters . At NYSE Technologies, he will report to Dominique Cerutti, president and deputy CEO of NYSE Euronext.  “He brings considerable industry experience and proven
leadership in building and managing innovative, customer focused
global technology solutions,” Cerutti said in a press statement
today.  Bloomberg LP, the parent of Bloomberg News, competes with
Thomson Reuters in selling financial and legal information and
trading systems.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rita Nazareth in New York at 
